Project Skills

##
Claude Code skills specific to TraChronic.

###
Available Skills

####
Release
Runs the TraChronic Swift release process for TestFlight alpha builds. Executes pre-release checks (tests, git state), then triggers the Deploy Swift to TestFlight workflow.

Triggers when:

* User asks to release, deploy, or ship a build to TestFlight
* User asks to "cut a build" or "release alpha"
* See release/SKILL.md for the full procedure.

Adding New Skills

* Create skill via the skill-creator skill in Claude Code.
* Drop the packaged skill into .claude/skills/<your-skill-name>/.
* Commit so the team can use it.
